    "0": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "# 🛠️ Tech Support & Dev — Application Health & Performance Dashboard\n\n**Application:** [APP_NAME] (`APPLICATION-XXXXXXXXXXXX`) | **Data Source:** Gen 3 RUM (`user.events`), Metrics\n\n**[CLIENT_NAME] — Company — Company Objectives Tracked:**\n\n| Objective | KPIs on this Dashboard |\n|-----------|------------------------|\n| **Ensure Platform Reliability** | Total errors, error rate trend, first-party vs third-party split |\n| **Deliver Fast Digital Experience** | Core Web Vitals (LCP, FCP, INP, CLS, TTFB) with Google thresholds |\n| **Reduce Customer-Impacting Bugs** | Top JS exceptions, top first-party errors, sessions affected |\n| **Maintain Booking Flow Integrity** | Booking SPA errors, API error rates, 500/404 breakdowns |\n| **Optimise Third-Party Dependencies** | Third-party error volume, worst ad-tech / analytics failures |\n\n> **Usage:** Use this dashboard to triage errors, monitor Core Web Vitals against Google SLO thresholds, and prioritise bug fixes by session impact. Timeframe defaults to 24h for cost efficiency."
    },
